    • addFirst

      public void addFirst(String segment)
      Inserts the specified segment at the beginning of the path.

      This is functionally equivalent to segments.addFirst(segment) and allows the path to behave like a deque or a rooted IRI path starting with a new segment.

      Parameters:
      segment - the segment to add at the head of the path
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if the segment is null
